<div class="about-page">
  <section id="about" class="row">

    <div class='col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1'>
      <h1>How can we create more opportunities for adult education?</h1>
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>Chalkle was started by Silvia Zuur and Linc Gasking within the Enspiral network as a successful meetup group in mid-2012 and has been supported to grow ever since.</p>
        <p>Our shared mission remains the same.</p>
        <p class="bold">To support more learning and teaching in our communities.</p>
        <p>Since 2012 we have worked with a range of partners and collaborators to test new models for supporting community learning. We built chalkle.com to help give anyone the resources and technology they need organise classes in their community.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-6 first-coffee">
      <%= image_tag asset_path("partners/first-coffee.jpg"), class: 'img' %>
    </div>

  </section>

