      </p>
      <p>
        Silvia Zuur, Linc Gasking, Joshua Vial, Brandon Mikel, Leticia Murillo Esteban, Amy Peng, Kiesia Carmine,
        Nanz Nair, Nicola Price, Hannah Varnell, Liz Willoughby-Martin, Craig Ambrose, Anthony Cabraal, Mitzi Borren,
        Sandra Otto, Karen Lee, Jack Tolley, Matthew Kerr, Josh Dean, Genevieve Parkes.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="col-xs-6">
      <h2>Open to partnerships</h2>
      <p>If you're interested in supporting our work, partnering or contributing to the next wave of solutions for adult education in New Zealand or further afield, we would love to connect.</p>
      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="mailto:hello@chalkle.com" class='btn btn-primary say-hello-btn'>hello@chalkle.com</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>
